sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant SWS
  participant Gateway as UdyogSetu Gateway
  participant Adapter as Adapter Runtime
  participant Dept as Department System
  participant Kafka
  participant Orch as Orchestration
  participant Investor as Investor Dashboard
  SWS->>Gateway: Submit canonical case update
  Gateway->>Orch: Validate transition request
  Orch->>Kafka: Publish case/task event
  Orch->>Adapter: Queue southbound delivery
  Adapter->>Dept: submitApplication / pushDocument
  Dept-->>Adapter: acknowledgement + external reference
  Adapter->>Kafka: Publish acknowledgement event
  Kafka->>Investor: Projection updates timeline
  Dept-->>Adapter: later status callback
  Adapter->>Orch: Normalised callback
  Orch->>Kafka: Publish task.status_changed.v1
  Kafka->>Investor: Dashboard refreshes unified status
